It's time to do absolutely everything we can to save our democracy.

If there's a vote, vote Democrat. I don't care how lame they are, they are the only non-fascist option that has any hope of winning any election. I don't care what lame excuse you have for not voting or voting third-party, at this point, anyone who isn't voting Democrat is SUPPORTING FASCISM. And speaking as a progressive with vanishingly little representation in this country, it sucks. But I vote Dem because it's the only sane thing to do.

If there's a protest, get out if you can. I'm a wheelchair user and I can't always, but I am when I can. Protest by itself does little, same with talking about these issues: But talking builds community, protest shows people are willing to get out there and speak up. These are necessary foundational steps to what we need to do, which is to take action and make changes. So these things are critical.

We need to use every single tool at our disposal against fascism. The norms are already gone. I don't like violene; I don't like politics; but you know what I hate more? Fascism.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4IWIKvZ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[daychilde]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>#butlerianjihad</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PwX4wwJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/l7GLeLm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PwX4wwJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Freyja33]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>MAGA - They Live. Obey. Consume. Submit.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ytL5YPs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ROfL90S.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sacrifice your healthcare to make billionaires richer.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ytL5YPs</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[t1mac]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Heil Satan</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/uxlWJst</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5uXzm7S.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/uxlWJst</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[crcb]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Good parenting</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JY0cuY4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4xGFFmo.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JY0cuY4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CitizenK9]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Imagine cooking dinner for the 800 best chefs in the world</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/sEythgE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DuqPcMM.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><sp